  <ThingDef ParentName="BaseWeapon">
    <defName>Melee_VibrosonicKatana</defName>
    <label>vibrosonic katana</label>
    <description>An exclusive two handed katana with its blade edge made of vibrosonic solution. Vibrosonic solution has a hidden EMP properties which is essential against mechanoids, and at the hands of a professional swordsman, the katana is capable of performing multiple sword slashes with variying damages. Due to the rarity of vibrosonic solution, only a handful of these katanas are manufactured and only sold on a premium price.</description>
